DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
1287::$$$message_0010_0000_0000$$$::Well, it might be good to see how Fuji-nee's doing, sort of a way to get in some light after-meal exercise.[lr]::
1288::$$$message_0010_0000_0001$$$::"Yeah. I'll try getting back at her for telling Sakura that embarrassing story."::
1289::$$$message_0010_0001_0000$$$::"Hm? Oh, I thought you were taking a bath."[lr]::
1290::$$$message_0010_0001_0001$$$::Fuji-nee is silently peeling tangerines, eating them for dessert.[lr]::
1291::$$$message_0010_0001_0002$$$::Two tangerine peels shaped like floating flowers are lying on top of the table.::
1292::$$$message_0010_0002_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
1293::$$$message_0010_0002_0001$$$::I feel like she's been cursed or something. She can't peel apples to save her life, but her tangerine peels are like works of art.::
1294::$$$message_0010_0003_0000$$$::"I've decided to take a bath later. I've got a bone to pick with you about the stories you told earlier."[lr]::
1295::$$$message_0010_0003_0001$$$::"What? Oh, let it go, will you? That stuff was from a long time ago and Sakura was real happy to hear about it. Anyway...here. You need to fulfill your quota. You gotta eat at least one a day."[lr]::
1296::$$$message_0010_0003_0002$$$::She takes a small tangerine out from a basket on the table and tosses it to me.::
1297::$$$message_0010_0004_0000$$$::"Whoa. Hey, you're not gonna win me over with a tangerine.[lr]::
1298::$$$message_0010_0004_0001$$$::It's a good thing you only told Sakura, but never tell stories like that at school. People like Issei would be concerned. It wouldn't be good."::
1299::$$$message_0010_0005_0000$$$::"I bet Mitsuzuri would be rolling on the floor laughing if she heard the story. Kidding, kidding. I know. I won't talk about your childhood other than to Sakura."::
1300::$$$message_0010_0006_0000$$$::"That's not my point. I'm saying don't talk about it to Sakura either. I'm sure Sakura doesn't like hearing boring-ass stories like that. And...I know you won't do it again, but if you do, I'll get real mad."[lr]::
1301::$$$message_0010_0006_0001$$$::I glare at Fuji-nee with all my might, showing how serious I am.::
1302::$$$message_0010_0007_0000$$$::"Ohhh. Oh I see. I get it. So that's what this is about, Shirou."[lr]::
1303::$$$message_0010_0007_0001$$$::Despite my efforts, Fuji-nee grins, clearly pleased with herself.::
1304::$$$message_0010_0008_0000$$$::"Oh, for... You're really starting to piss me off. Why do you look so pleased with yourself, you dumb tiger?"[lr]::
1305::$$$message_0010_0008_0001$$$::I scowl angrily at Fuji-nee.::
1306::$$$message_0010_0009_0000$$$::"You can call me tiger all you want. But let me get this straight: you didn't want Sakura to hear that story.[lr]::
1307::$$$message_0010_0009_0001$$$::You don't care if anyone else knows you want to become a champion of justice. But you're embarrassed about Sakura finding out."[lr]::
1308::$$$message_0010_0009_0002$$$::"Wha...!"[lr]::
1309::$$$message_0010_0009_0003$$$::Th-that's not...true... I think.::
1310::$$$message_0010_0010_0000$$$::"Okay, okay. Theeen...I'm gonna keep on blabbing.[lr]::
1311::$$$message_0010_0010_0001$$$::Awww, Shirou has finally noticed Sakura.[lr]::
1312::$$$message_0010_0010_0002$$$::I'm a little concerned as an educator, but I'm relieved as your guardian. And at the same time, I might be a little heartbroken as your big sister."::
1313::$$$message_0010_0011_0000$$$::Her speech is almost weirdly emotional, and then half a heartbeat later, she shoves a whole tangerine into her mouth.[lr]::
1314::$$$message_0010_0011_0001$$$::Fuji-nee can fit anything up to the size of her fist in her mouth.[lr]::
1315::$$$message_0010_0011_0002$$$::An act like that might be alluring if we were in the wild savanna or something, but such feral charm seems kind of unbecoming for a mature woman like her.::
1316::$$$message_0010_0012_0000$$$::"Oh? Weren't you taking a bath?"[lr]::
1317::$$$message_0010_0012_0001$$$::In comes Sakura.[lr]::
1318::$$$message_0010_0012_0002$$$::She heads right into the living room, having finished up with the dishes.::
1319::$$$message_0010_0013_0000$$$::"I put it off because there was something I had to talk to Fuji-nee about. Want a tangerine, Sakura?"[lr]::
1320::$$$message_0010_0013_0001$$$::I reach over for the stack of tangerines in a basket.[lr]::
1321::$$$message_0010_0013_0002$$$::It's unexpected, but the three of us relaxing together after dinner is kind of nice.::
1322::$$$message_0010_0014_0000$$$::"Oh, Ms. Fujimura offered me some already. She saved some just for me, and they were delicious."[lr]::
1323::$$$message_0010_0014_0001$$$::"Sakura doesn't like to eat fresh fruit.[lr]::
1324::$$$message_0010_0014_0002$$$::She can only eat them if they're cooked or frozen like ice cream. Oh hey, isn't it getting late, Sakura?"::
1325::$$$message_0010_0015_0000$$$::"Yes. I've finished cleaning up, so I'll be heading home now."[lr]::
1326::$$$message_0010_0015_0001$$$::"Got it. I guess it's time for me to go too. Let's go together, Sakura. I'll walk you home since it's been dangerous outside lately."::
1327::$$$message_0010_0016_0000$$$::Fuji-nee halts her mass consumption of tangerines and gets to her feet, somehow managing to look bold.[lr]::
1328::$$$message_0010_0016_0001$$$::The way she gets up gives the impression of a responsible elder.::
1329::$$$message_0010_0017_0000$$$::"Eh...are you sure?"[lr]::
1330::$$$message_0010_0017_0001$$$::"Of course. I'm responsible for both you and Shirou, so I need to make sure you get home safe. You don't mind, right, Shirou? Don't forget to lock up once the two of us leave."::
1331::$$$message_0010_0018_0000$$$::"Got it. As long as you're with Sakura, I won't worry, even if you're attacked by perverts...or bears."[lr]::
1332::$$$message_0010_0018_0001$$$::"I don't know about bears. Not sure I can do much against a bear, so Sakura and I will run right back here if that happens. Then the two of us will beat the bear up together and we'll have bear stew for dinner the next day."::
1333::$$$message_0010_0019_0000$$$::Fuji-nee smiles fearlessly.[lr]::
1334::$$$message_0010_0019_0001$$$::...Yeah.[lr]::
1335::$$$message_0010_0019_0002$$$::Fuji-nee typically marches to a different beat...a beat so loud and discordant it wreaks havoc on everything around her, but as a teacher, she's also so courageous it's almost admirable."::
1336::$$$message_0010_0020_0000$$$::"Let's go, Sakura. See ya tomorrow, Shirou."[lr]::
1337::$$$message_0010_0020_0001$$$::"Have a good night, Senpai."[lr]::
1338::$$$message_0010_0020_0002$$$::"Yep."[lr]::
1339::$$$message_0010_0020_0003$$$::The two leave the mansion.[lr]::
1340::$$$message_0010_0020_0004$$$::I see them off from the front door, and then I lock the door behind them, as instructed by Fuji-nee.::

